OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA widely dry and sunny day with
OL,6,Fany early morning low cloud and mist
OL,7,Fsoon clearing. Feeling very warm,
OL,8,Fespecially in the strong sunshine. A
OL,9,Fgentle easterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FPlenty of late evening
OL,12,Fsunshine to end Wednesday. Low cloud
OL,13,Freturning overnight and becoming misty
OL,14,Fover higher ground. A mild night.
OL,15,
OL,16,CThursday:FAnother fine, dry and very
OL,17,Fwarm day. Any morning low cloud once
OL,18,Fagain quickly clearing to leave
OL,19,Fprolonged periods of strong sunshine
OL,20,Fthroughout Thursday. Calm winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
